Class Duration

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.Abhigya.core.util.Duration
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConfigurableDuration

    public class Duration
extends java.lang.Object
    A duration that can be converted to milliseconds, seconds, minutes, hours or days.
